videos.headline: Temple takes lead off Thomas' 15-yard score
videos.description: Temple runs an end around for RB Jahad Thomas who rushes 15 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Temple QB Walker finds Bryant for a 22-yard TD
videos.description: Temple QB Phillip Walker drops back and throws to an open Ventell Bryant for a 22-yard touchdown to extend the Owls' lead over Navy.

videos.headline: Temple forces Navy fumble
videos.description: Toneo Gulley fumbled, forced by Sean Chandler, recovered by Temple's Avery Williams

videos.headline: Temple's 56-yard TD puts them up by three scores
videos.description: Temple QB Phillip Walker throws a deep pass complete to Keith Kirkwood for a 56-yard touchdown, putting the Owls up 21-0 over Navy.

videos.headline: Temple's Avery Williams ejected for targeting
videos.description: Temple's Avery Williams ejected for targeting
